Magaaladu waxay ku taallaa xeebta Mjøsa, waa magaalo weyn oo Norway ah, waana magaalada ugu weyn ee magaalada Hedmark. Waxaa xaafadaha waqooyi-galbeed ee waqooyi galbeed kaga yaal degmada Ringsaker, waqooyiga by Åmot, bari ee Løten, iyo koonfurta ee Stange.
